# Available Test Rules

Use these keywords to generate unit tests:

| Keyword | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `@test-aov` | Create a unit test to display a specific AOV buffer (depth, primId, Neye, color, elementId, instanceId) |
| `@test-task` | Create a unit test with a single frame pass and custom tasks (blur, FXAA, SSAO, etc.) |

## Usage Examples

### AOV Display Tests
```
@test-aov depth
@test-aov primId
@test-aov Neye
```

### Custom Task Tests
```
@test-task blur
@test-task fxaa
@test-task SSAO
```

## Notes

- Both rules will ask which file to add the test to before generating code
- Generated tests include a `// Prompt:` comment documenting the original request
- Tests follow the established patterns in the codebase with proper GPU synchronization and image validation
